Greetings-<br>
<br>
As I was doing my Karana scouting tonight, I happened upon some strange events in South Karana. Am not sure what this has to do with war, if anything, but figured you would like to know anything amiss. Three named undead gnolls, Triza the Dead, Gezra the Dead, and Braza the Dead up and started wandering around. The strange thing about this is that high-level characters could not kill them, and it was up to a few 20ish PCs to wipe them out. My partner Yarlin and I were attacked a bit south of Infected Paw, as Triza said,&quot;Join us in DEATH. Join us in eternal PAIN.&quot; 2 Were confirmed dead, leaving the leader Triza at large. I asked if any notes or scrolls were found, but no clear answer was recieving. Anyhow, I'd hate to think that the gnolls are involved in the great War to come, but coincidence seems too unlikely in these final days of peace.<br>
<br>
