c) this is no real news, just something i would like you to know, i raised my skill at fletching to 202 yesterday, which means i can nearly perfectly make even the best arrows and i can also make trueshots and darkwood bows with a very high success rate, so if anyone needs something of that, tell me<br>
<br>
thank you again for reading<br>
